code: /**  * Returns a live reference to the list of cipher suite names.  *  * @return a reference to the list, never {@code null}  */ public List<String> getCipherSuite() {     if (this.cipherSuite == null) {         this.cipherSuite = new ArrayList<>().     }     return this.cipherSuite. }
